                "version": "2.6.2",
                "change_log": "VRidge 2.6\n- Improved picture compression quality.\n- Improved color accuracy, especially in dark scenes.\n- Reduced latency on Nvidia cards.\n- Implemented multiple ways to reduce mid-stream artifacting.\n- Reduced continous audio delay that could be triggered by intermittent lags."
            },
            {
                "version": "2.5.0",
                "change_log": "2.5.0\n- Gamewarp option - new way to interact with non-VR games.\n- Configurable gamma correction.\n- Improved compatibility with new GeForce and Radeon cards.\n\n\nRead about the full list of changes in our most recent blog entry at blog.riftcat.com"
            },
